{"tid":2119083,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"淨空法師被指「危害國安 歪理邪說」 中共焚佛經 僧人轟如文革","createTime":"2020-07-22T02:04:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T06:16:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6c647aa87de0e4a60c068329f4e21a60a12c0994","tid":2119083,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T02:04:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200722/CFT7WB55N7QDAS3B2YJ2XLOFAM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200722%2FCFT7WB55N7QDAS3B2YJ2XLOFAM%2F&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtB5S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=6cc70408\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200722%2FCFT7WB55N7QDAS3B2YJ2XLOFAM%2F&h=8da9f64a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200722/CFT7WB55N7QDAS3B2YJ2XLOFAM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n淨空法師被指「危害國安 歪理邪說」<br />\n中共焚佛經 僧人轟如文革<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/nYWZHTw8VMiquKUBq5r6mOEGgds=/1502x725/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AISH4P53TV2MW34U2OMKONGLSI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FnYWZHTw8VMiquKUBq5r6mOEGgds%3D%2F1502x725%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAISH4P53TV2MW34U2OMKONGLSI.gif&h=c24ae801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n習近平上任後宗教被迫「姓黨」的情況加劇。<br />\n<br />\n內地各處的宗教長期被打壓，關注中國宗教情況的網絡雜誌《寒冬（Bitter Winter） 》報道指，在台灣修佛的淨空法師被認為「危害國家安全」，故地方接命令銷毀所有與他有關的書籍。在吉林的佛教圖書館也獲告知，鑑於香港局勢動亂，需要清除香港和台灣等境外來的外國書籍，有中國僧人直指現在的情況有如文革一樣，「這就是法難啊﹗」<br />\n<br />\n習近平上任後強調「宗教姓黨」，內地加強打壓各大宗教，就算在武漢肺炎肆虐的半年間，力度從沒減少，基督教會被取締、穆斯林被強迫不守齋戒，《寒冬》前日再揭露佛教書籍被下令要清理。吉林省一家佛教圖書館所有境外出版的書籍，。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/K1SQmjzOCmxZus9S76DNO_E2l-Y=/190x113/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SBP4EZ3MABZZXQHZUHPIBSWWAU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FK1SQmjzOCmxZus9S76DNO_E2l-Y%3D%2F190x113%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSBP4EZ3MABZZXQHZUHPIBSWWAU.gif&h=7eddcc3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣的慧律法師和證嚴法師著作都被禁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Bkvmt8ca5JZUo2V0-rPmjLMv2wA=/469x281/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/S7FJ4JVSCVTXUMRQ6S74IABGWA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBkvmt8ca5JZUo2V0-rPmjLMv2wA%3D%2F469x281%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FS7FJ4JVSCVTXUMRQ6S74IABGWA.gif&h=95057f7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n淨空法師的書籍被認為「危害國家安全」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港台海外書籍同被下架<br />\n<br />\n一名山東佛堂負責人指，自己被要求清除未經過中國當局批准、沒有國家簽發出版號的書籍，「和文化大革命時期中共砸佛像、。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/nBrKZkqHWFNmyTKDCWkBnOBb8jU=/190x300/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CGTCOOFW6I4TO2374RCZCNYHVU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FnBrKZkqHWFNmyTKDCWkBnOBb8jU%3D%2F190x300%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCGTCOOFW6I4TO2374RCZCNYHVU.gif&h=863faaa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「不聽國家話 寺廟也被封」<br />\n<br />\n一名被查抄的寺廟住持告訴《寒冬》，「國家說淨空法師配合西方反中，他的書『危害國家安全』，必須焚燒。」 儘管。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n除了淨空，同樣在台灣講佛的慈濟基金會創辦人證嚴法師也榜上有名。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n《寒冬》"},{"pid":"47dccccbffe92e0b1e256d2e1915ccc58926b342","tid":2119083,"uid":24788,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T02:09:25.000Z","msg":"你佛教算老幾<br />\n天主教都要聽黨話呀"},{"pid":"1b8ff9dff17b78cae6852a3f21a0f7f70eec4952","tid":2119083,"uid":72058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T02:10:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40fffb7e55e8c986e30eb3b1068c35ae0cca3dbc","tid":2119083,"uid":29798,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T02:20:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HmIW0SWx35A&amp;feature=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHmIW0SWx35A%26feature%3Dshare&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtB5S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=e00c4946\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HmIW0SWx35A&amp;feature=share</a><br />\n<br />\n淨空法師曾經指維尼係再世菩薩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f118a5a8e6bedebcc1345c2f11bc46a33dd1a1","tid":2119083,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40fffb7e55e8c986e30eb3b1068c35ae0cca3dbc","tid":2119083,"uid":29798,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T02:20:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HmIW0SWx35A&amp;feature=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHmIW0SWx35A%26feature%3Dshare&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtB5S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=e00c4946\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HmIW0SWx35A&amp;feature=share</a><br />\n<br />\n淨空法師曾經指維尼係再世菩薩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T02:46:13.000Z","msg":"聽完真係明白咩叫謠言惑眾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7531f5e7c1496d0693e742ef2ab040d48504b11","tid":2119083,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T02:46:19.000Z","msg":"CLS <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29df03edcccbb9cef1f491656e6a99